## Appendix A: Complete Gadget Library

### A.1 Basic Logical Gadgets

**AND Gate:**
$$H_{\text{AND}}(a,b,out) = (ab - out)^2$$

**OR Gate:**
$$H_{\text{OR}}(a,b,out) = (a + b - ab - out)^2$$

**XOR Gate:**
$$H_{\text{XOR}}(a,b,out) = (a + b - 2ab - out)^2$$

**NOT Gate:**
$$H_{\text{NOT}}(a,out) = (1 - a - out)^2$$

### A.2 Arithmetic Gadgets

**Half Adder:**
$$H_{\text{HA}}(a,b,s,c) = (a + b - s - 2c)^2$$

**Full Adder:**
$$H_{\text{FA}}(a,b,c_{in},s,c_{out}) = (a + b + c_{in} - s - 2c_{out})^2$$

**Comparator:**
$$H_{\text{CMP}}(a,b,gt,eq,lt) = (a - b - gt + lt)^2 + (a \oplus b \oplus eq)^2$$

### A.3 Constraint Gadgets

**Exactly-1 (One-Hot):**
$$H_{\text{one-hot}}(x_1,\ldots,x_n) = \left(\sum_{i=1}^n x_i - 1\right)^2 + \sum_{i<j} x_i x_j$$

**At-Most-1:**
$$H_{\text{atmost1}}(x_1,\ldots,x_n) = \sum_{i<j} x_i x_j$$

**At-Least-1:**
$$H_{\text{atleast1}}(x_1,\ldots,x_n) = 1 - \prod_{i=1}^n (1-x_i)$$

